                     <interp inst="t18431127-210-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing 2lbs. weight of mut<lb></lb>ton, value 9<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18431127-name-1160" type="victimName">
